## Environment setup
virtualenv --no-site-packages venv
pip install Flask -E venv/
source venv/bin/activate
pip install requests

## Configure
cp config_template.py config.py
<Edit as necessary.  Defaults should work on your local machine hosting the capability container.>

## Run
python main.py

point your browser to http://localhost:3000

## Current features (in progress)


- Flask powered API (using mock data)

- New js/css for R2 screens (moving away from original js/css/img from ooici-pres



## Usage (see SETUP before these steps)

- Run flask powered api/webserver 
    $ python main.py
